T1  - Convex costs and the hedging paradox
AU  - Frestad, Dennis
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 16
IS  - 2
SP  - 236
EP  - 242
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/04/01/
SN  - 0929-1199
